        "evidence": "<p>Addition of selected points.</p>\n<p><strong>Useful mnemonic: PANCREAS</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>PaO2 &lt;7.9 kPa</li>\n<li>Age &gt;55 years</li>\n<li>Neutrophils (WBC &gt;15 x 10⁹/L)</li>\n<li>Calcium &lt;2 mmol/L</li>\n<li>Renal function: Urea &gt;16 mmol/L</li>\n<li>Enzymes LDH &gt;600 IU/L</li>\n<li>Albumin &lt;32 g/L (serum)</li>\n<li>Sugar (blood glucose) &gt;10 mmol/L</li>\n</ul>",
        "facts": "<p><strong>Score interpretation:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n<table class=\"table table-bordered table-hover\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">Score</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">Number of patients (in original study)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: center;\">Severe Pancreatitis*</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">101</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">125</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">87</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">16%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">49</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">20%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">28</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">61%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">11</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">55%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">100%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">0%</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">100%</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>*PPV of 79% in original study</p>\n</div>",
        "estimation": [],
